raw_body: AL HAJ MOHAMED MOHAMED KALEEL – (Chairman of Jewelarts Group of Companies and Chairman of Kollupitiya Jumma Masjid) passed away on the 6th August 2023. He was the beloved husband of Hajiani Fathima Ayna Kaleel,​ much loved father of Nishreen,​ Ahamed,​ Akif and Nushrath,​ father-in-law of Ishan,​ Hiraz,​ Dilani and Ayman,​ loving brother of Marhoom Mohamed Zawahir,​ Mohamed Hilmy,​ Mohamed Izzath Mohamed Zahool,​ Enya Shaheed,​ Feroza Muzammil & Azha Shanawaz. Burial was done at Jawatte Jumma Masjid after the Janaza prayers conducted at Colpetty Jumma Mosque on the 6th August 2023.051228
